<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TypeCast Payment</title>
    <script src="https://js.stripe.com/v3/"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-9aIt2nRpC12Uk9gS9baDl411NQApFmC26EwAOH8WgZl5MYYxFfc+NcPb1dKGj7Sk" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <!-- JS, Popper.js, and jQuery -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-DfXdz2htPH0lsSSs5nCTpuj/zy4C+OGpamoFVy38MVBnE+IbbVYUew+OrCXaRkfj" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-OgVRvuATP1z7JjHLkuOU7Xw704+h835Lr+6QL9UvYjZE3Ipu6Tp75j7Bh/kR0JKI" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <style>
        .responsive-img{
            width:60%;
            height:70%;
        }
        @media screen and (max-width: 778px) {
            .responsive-img{
                width:100%;
                height:100%
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include("partials/navbar") %>
    <div style="padding-bottom:20px;"></div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="responsive-img" style="margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">
            <img class="responsive-img" src="/images/UnderConstruction.jpg" alt="Under Construction">
        </div>
        <div style="padding-bottom:20px;"></div>

        <div class="container">
            <ul class="list-group">
                <li class="list-group-item clearfix">
                    <h3 class="list-group-item-heading" style="text-align: center;">
                        We are currently under construction:
                    </h3>
                    <p class="list-group-item-text lead" style="text-align: center;">
                        But dont worry! There is still something you can do!
                    </p>
                    <p class="list-group-item-text lead">
                        While we are under construction, we can still use your support! If you pay now, you will get a special bonus!
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li class="list-group-item clearfix">
                    <h3 class="list-group-item-heading" style="text-align: center;">
                        Benefits Of Paying Now:
                    </h3>
                    <p class="list-group-item-text lead" style="text-align: center;">
                        If you pay today, you will get a premium membership for limited amount of time.
                    </p>
                  </li>

                <li class="list-group-item clearfix">
                    <h3 class="list-group-item-heading" style="text-align: center;">
                        Payments:
                    </h3>
                    <p class="list-group-item-text lead" style="text-align: center;">
                        <span style="font-weight: bold;"><i>NOTE:</span></i> If payments arent currently working, please try back again soon as that should be functional any
                        day now!
                    </p>
                    <div class='container' style="text-align:center;">
                        <a href="#"><img src="/images/stripe.png" alt="Under Construction" style="width:200px; height:40px;"></a>
                    </div>
                </li>

            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>